    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Good is a short (1-2 hours!) linear narrative adventure with replayable minigames. Skip class, avoid your crush, and refuse to participate in anything useful. Jam to the music, enjoy the programmer art, stay up late. Real late. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/58c77558776fcbdfe92ed19f4185176d.poster.avif?t=1756131393\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/58c77558776fcbdfe92ed19f4185176d.webm?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/58c77558776fcbdfe92ed19f4185176d.mp4?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Batting practice</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The minigame that started it all. Hit some dingers! You get 10 tries. You’ll want more than 10. Maximum score is 3,000, some say it’s impossible.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/afb785c89b8e176515dd8d0d8336fbaf.poster.avif?t=1756131393\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/afb785c89b8e176515dd8d0d8336fbaf.webm?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/afb785c89b8e176515dd8d0d8336fbaf.mp4?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dream on</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partake in some light platforming. This was supposed to be a platformer? These levels are only here so the jump button makes sense.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/52eb57611bc0eca98f6a32e9738473d3.poster.avif?t=1756131393\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/52eb57611bc0eca98f6a32e9738473d3.webm?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/52eb57611bc0eca98f6a32e9738473d3.mp4?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Track Meet</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Test your high speed precision with a variety of track and field events.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/d17c4078076d81fdb82c4a9d6b8ae540.poster.avif?t=1756131393\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/d17c4078076d81fdb82c4a9d6b8ae540.webm?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/d17c4078076d81fdb82c4a9d6b8ae540.mp4?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Catch some waves</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They say surfing is hard. It is! The advent of video games are supposed to make sports like surfing much easier, but where’s the fun in that?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/c5bc30c1cdb0180a07a20daa6ef6987c.poster.avif?t=1756131393\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/c5bc30c1cdb0180a07a20daa6ef6987c.webm?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3165530/extras/c5bc30c1cdb0180a07a20daa6ef6987c.mp4?t=1756131393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Make friends</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More minigames!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crude Humor</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A (short) story of a day in the life of an American high-schooler  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovely programmer pixel-art </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Completely original soundtrack </p></li></ul>",
